  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Countless souls wander the ring road at night.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The title of “fastest” never fades, no matter how times change.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The stage of battle is a sealed future Tokyo.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Race through the night highways weaving through the city in your customized machine.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Defeat the countless rivals and aim to become the fastest on the Shuto Expressway.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A One-of-a-Kind SP Battle</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A unique system that sets itself apart from other racing games.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In battles where drivers clash by reducing “Spirit Points,” a numerical measure of mental strength, speed alone is not enough to secure victory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Strategy is required to wear down your opponent’s Spirit Points — an experience where only the rules for winning matter.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A Realistic Experience Linked to Reality</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 30 officially licensed manufacturers are featured, including real-world vehicles and aero parts.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy the thrill of speed on faithfully recreated courses of the Shuto Expressway.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2634950/extras/e62ee4b50ec209c0935efe5ab541e6fb.avif?t=1772290875\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2634950/extras/3178a2953992eca7169cdffe53b44e19.avif?t=1772290875\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2634950/extras_big/3178a2953992eca7169cdffe53b44e19.avif?t=1772290875 width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Customize to Your Style</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enhance performance through tuning and refine driving feel with detailed settings to create your ultimate machine.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A wide range of customization options — including vinyl graphics, stickers, and body colors — let you personalize your ride.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2634950/extras/8d1aad90a5f529a87960ce175f5e2de3.avif?t=1772290875\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2634950/extras_big/8d1aad90a5f529a87960ce175f5e2de3.avif?t=1772290875 width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2634950/extras/cac4a7f5717356ba675373fe09f9789d.avif?t=1772290875\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2634950/extras_big/cac4a7f5717356ba675373fe09f9789d.avif?t=1772290875 width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Stories of Unique Rivals</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A world where over 450 rivals clash in pursuit of supremacy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Even those battling for the top reveal their true selves during moments of respite at parking areas.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Souls driven by the desire to be “the fastest” are drawn together, sometimes colliding as they create their own rhythm.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Witness the birth of a new “legend” with your own eyes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2634950/extras/6802b93068ac47f1ff1c7305b11bf4cc.avif?t=1772290875\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2634950/extras_big/6802b93068ac47f1ff1c7305b11bf4cc.avif?t=1772290875 width=1560 height=834 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2634950/extras/8ff116297f9c0cdc41f2d3187234a61c.avif?t=1772290875\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2634950/extras_big/8ff116297f9c0cdc41f2d3187234a61c.avif?t=1772290875 width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2634950/extras/b482834a80fc9b81e30dde0031e48973.avif?t=1772290875\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2634950/extras_big/b482834a80fc9b81e30dde0031e48973.webp?t=1772290875 width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2634950/extras/54a763696a2f30d21e68e8ef3ea12c58.avif?t=1772290875\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2634950/extras_big/54a763696a2f30d21e68e8ef3ea12c58.avif?t=1772290875 width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >New Feature in This Title: The “PERK” System</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A skill-tree system that allows you to unlock various functions using BP earned from winning battles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Permanently enhance driver abilities, increase rewards, and improve convenience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2634950/extras/4e4fd4de80e486a671a0443a1d9e9608.avif?t=1772290875\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2634950/extras_big/4e4fd4de80e486a671a0443a1d9e9608.avif?t=1772290875 width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2634950/extras/d6bf126e20307a5e7d9f25e3ce216d29.avif?t=1772290875\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Steering Wheel Controller Support</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Devices without preset configurations can also be fully customized through key configuration in the options menu.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >* Fanatec® CSL DD wheel base</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >* HORI® Wireless Racing Wheel Apex for PlayStation®4 / PC</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >* HORI® Force Feedback Truck Control System for Windows® PC</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >* HORI® Force Feedback Racing Wheel DLX for PlayStation®5 / PlayStation®4 / PC</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >* Logicool G® G29 Driving Force</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >* Logicool G® G923 TRUEFORCE Racing Wheel</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >* Logicool G® RS50</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >* MOZA R5 DD wheel base</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >* Thrustmaster® T248</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >* Thrustmaster® T300 RS</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >* Thrustmaster® T598</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Countless souls wander the ring road at night.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The title of “fastest” never fades, no matter how times change.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The stage of battle is a sealed future Tokyo.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Race through the night highways weaving through the city in your customized machine.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Defeat the countless rivals and aim to become the fastest on the Shuto Expressway.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A One-of-a-Kind SP Battle</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A unique system that sets itself apart from other racing games.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In battles where drivers clash by reducing “Spirit Points,” a numerical measure of mental strength, speed alone is not enough to secure victory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Strategy is required to wear down your opponent’s Spirit Points — an experience where only the rules for winning matter.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A Realistic Experience Linked to Reality</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 30 officially licensed manufacturers are featured, including real-world vehicles and aero parts.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy the thrill of speed on faithfully recreated courses of the Shuto Expressway.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2634950/extras/e62ee4b50ec209c0935efe5ab541e6fb.avif?t=1772290875\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2634950/extras/3178a2953992eca7169cdffe53b44e19.avif?t=1772290875\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2634950/extras_big/3178a2953992eca7169cdffe53b44e19.avif?t=1772290875 width=15